<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The tokenizer in Zend_Reflection_File ignores T_INTERFACE so it is not possible to reflect interfaces within files at the moment. Zend_Reflection_Class inherits ReflectionClass thus it should be possible to reflect interfaces.</p>

<p>Zend_CodeGenerator_Php_Class assumes that Zend_Reflection_Class is always a class. So it is not possible to generate an interface.</p>

